岗位包括快递员、送餐员等，工作内容相对简单，上手更快，因此企业的招聘要求最为宽松。蓝领岗位需求大，部分城市快递外卖员平均月薪超八千元 _ 招聘 _ 职业 _ 配送"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-63ac5be825bb7fe4ad60112ae99cfbb4_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "39 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/658298820"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I0pzX3/unor9/EAMaCTEwODU2Njc3MyCtz4mzBjAAOFxAEnIJNjU4Mjk4ODIweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1717802428.683880", "card_id": "Q_658012468", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 119}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "领导喜欢「听话」的员工还是「有主见」的员工？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "听话的员工：领导让干什么就干什么，不管对错。但是如果出了问题由领导负责。 有主见的员工：有自己的主意和想法，如果觉得领导的命令不妥或者自己很难完成会主动提出来。但是自己有担当精神。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "38 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/658012468"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI0pzX3/unor9/EAMaCTEwODUwMjk1MCCi7PeyBjAAOKQBQBNyCTY1ODAxMjQ2OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1717802428.684374", "card_id": "Q_656142359", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 46}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "下属不好带，想放弃他，但是又担心大领导质疑我带人的能力，怎么办？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "38 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/656142359"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I0pzX3/unor9/EAMaCTEwODA4NzI0MiDM35SyBjAAOG5AFHIJNjU2MTQyMzU5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1717802428.684615", "card_id": "Q_658349513", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 4